This is a set of handy scripts:
* fullcheck: will check and tidy Perl scripts and modules
* functions: shell functions
* registrans_grabber: Perl script for data transform
* rename_lc : Perl script for bulk renaming of files to lowercase
* send_file : Perl for sending file as an email attachment
* sort_images_by: Images sorting tools (with two symlinks: sort_images_by_exifdate and sort_images_by_filename)
* ssh-to: wrapper for SSH connections
* urxvt: wrapper/launcher for urxvtc
